"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:44:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV"},{"pid":"e14aea2dd84f95d8b50283430ad7d38456b498da","tid":136302,"uid":62235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔，唔教抽血、打IV係一個RN Final year既fd話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1fc0d61336e35f7576f26bc3bb89667e8c0733e","tid":136302,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔，唔教抽血、打IV係一個RN Final year既fd話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRN都唔打IV抽血 仲有咩做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我會知EN連針都唔洗拎 (好似係) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce18ddd1512e5b6e03091f010e6243674f16bf8f","tid":136302,"uid":62235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T06:46:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔，唔教抽血、打IV係一個RN Final year既fd話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRN都唔打IV抽血 仲有咩做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我會知EN連針都唔洗拎 (好似係) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以咪個system 有問題，當你畢左業都係做Student nurse既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩，miss都會講一講，俾我地識下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ccb539db46a1b1c4f432366722f4a590e58529c","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:45:48.000Z","msg":"東華en面試有咩要注意？"},{"pid":"43b5ba6f768dac0a3b97a3189ff79202d7380e54","tid":136302,"uid":62235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T08:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東華en面試有咩要注意？</blockquote><br />\n記得帶個腦去，nursing interview會注重critical thinking 多d<br />\n<br />\n我上年有問中文同英文<br />\n英文題目已經唔記得左<br />\n中文題目：支唔支持標準工時立法"},{"pid":"8d7703affe7c410fb61452bc1b064eef141cc58b","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T09:43:25.000Z","msg":"有冇自我介紹？定直接黎討論？"},{"pid":"be3d94eb9d5d437b40963fc004f4b769e9e46e5c","tid":136302,"uid":81917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>全英 自我介紹加group discussion<br />\n個次我in其他都係女仔黎 都係著suit<br />\n雖然佢地英文都幾屎 但係個個唔係咩心臟科護士就物理治癒助理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果會8月尾左右先寄信比你 <br />\n冇記錯學費都好甘下<br />\n<br />\n利伸：2015dse 唔收我</blockquote><br />\n講野1999<br />\n難怪唔收你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我講堅喎 佢地真係咁自稱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  對唔住囉1999"},{"pid":"a8c22d893d433b02594dad29bfafaea4a9081ffe","tid":136302,"uid":52182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:13:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔，唔教抽血、打IV係一個RN Final year既fd話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRN都唔打IV抽血 仲有咩做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我會知EN連針都唔洗拎 (好似係) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據nc RN 真係唔駛識抽血同set IV<br />\n<br />\nha a&amp;e。私院都要拎張cert 先可以做wor"},{"pid":"535b0771ea825f866e977c7fa82f560cae587c04","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇自我介紹？定直接黎討論？</blockquote><br />\n？"},{"pid":"5b19e0c817f0ee0f7a109e170bbd822cc94b4e17","tid":136302,"uid":45746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔，唔教抽血、打IV係一個RN Final year既fd話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRN都唔打IV抽血 仲有咩做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我會知EN連針都唔洗拎 (好似係) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據nc RN 真係唔駛識抽血同set IV<br />\n<br />\nha a&amp;e。私院都要拎張cert 先可以做wor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nward有血姑打IV同抽血架嘛 好多RN都唔識"},{"pid":"cd7e46633821233cec8c2d6c9a3b253dfb4b840c","tid":136302,"uid":87173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:38:20.000Z","msg":"我上年in過en 同rn ，所以可能記錯d問題邊個打邊個。<br />\nen一開始就gp discussion （可以喺第一次講野嗰時講下自己咩名當自介），個discussion就用中文問同答，冇準備時間，問我地護士套制服代表d咩？之後用英文問左條問題（好似係單對單咁問），之後就完啦！之後就等email通知結果。"},{"pid":"94db5a1dbecfef737e50f2357beb99bb5a5cf43d","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我上年in過en 同rn ，所以可能記錯d問題邊個打邊個。<br />\nen一開始就gp discussion （可以喺第一次講野嗰時講下自己咩名當自介），個discussion就用中文問同答，冇準備時間，問我地護士套制服代表d咩？之後用英文問左條問題（好似係單對單咁問），之後就完啦！之後就等email通知結果。</blockquote><br />\n護士制服代表咩你點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"54783e191e52166e2117543da531b8865b7f28a2","tid":136302,"uid":44951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:42:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔，唔教抽血、打IV係一個RN Final year既fd話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRN都唔打IV抽血 仲有咩做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我會知EN連針都唔洗拎 (好似係) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據nc RN 真係唔駛識抽血同set IV<br />\n<br />\nha a&amp;e。私院都要拎張cert 先可以做wor</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nward有血姑打IV同抽血架嘛 好多RN都唔識</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nRN 無論邊到出黎都係唔會識抽血 打heparin block <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n病房通常都係抽血員或houseman 去做<br />\n<br />\n通常都係出到黎做 (如做急症室 )有需要老細會叫你讀<br />\n<br />\n不過真係好學既好多時都會搵識既人教你 偷下師咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f64297d3afece651b20efa743b4f35c22f0e6e4","tid":136302,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:49:03.000Z","msg":"收唔收男人？"},{"pid":"751cde3d35d5a00ff7eba53aa8733a2fedc8ef58","tid":136302,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T10:53:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>收唔收男人？</blockquote><br />\n上年都收唔小男 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但都係冇我份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d273e7a2d6286b6d06edd67eeba3f052f57d945","tid":136302,"uid":63875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"學店<br />\n校長系Marketing PHD ，但唔識做Marketing"},{"pid":"cd8c1c81e1648753f2b56e6c2155304c2291a17f","tid":136302,"uid":87173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我上年in過en 同rn ，所以可能記錯d問題邊個打邊個。<br />\nen一開始就gp discussion （可以喺第一次講野嗰時講下自己咩名當自介），個discussion就用中文問同答，冇準備時間，問我地護士套制服代表d咩？之後用英文問左條問題（好似係單對單咁問），之後就完啦！之後就等email通知結果。</blockquote><br />\n護士制服代表咩你點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n答責任團隊精神，專業嗰d。我嗰時遲左發言所以只可以執人口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dcab49d4783b865f73ca5742ea28a726ffb529a","tid":136302,"uid":285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T11:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我上年in過en 同rn ，所以可能記錯d問題邊個打邊個。<br />\nen一開始就gp discussion （可以喺第一次講野嗰時講下自己咩名當自介），個discussion就用中文問同答，冇準備時間，問我地護士套制服代表d咩？之後用英文問左條問題（好似係單對單咁問），之後就完啦！之後就等email通知結果。</blockquote><br />\n護士制服代表咩你點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n答責任團隊精神，專業嗰d。我嗰時遲左發言所以只可以執人口水尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常呢D問題 邊個答先就講哂 之後個D全部食哂屎咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca056c944f91307416f4d41b2f059b08643a0ca7","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:04:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人都聽日in ?"},{"pid":"50f119bb48e5c7cddaa5ec00b3020b0476f8c416","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-27T13:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ef014457465c7c6f11f9e362030fc35779a97b","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f796073b7ef7afdb73c48b5aefc354b565c29ab5","tid":136302,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84111b48812e3e46808c596cab5a39a