.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽日in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記住報告下問左咩 <br />\n我上年in 英文問中學選修科 中文問廢老金應否增加</blockquote><br />\nIn完</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問咩</blockquote><br />\n英文環節: 淨係每個人用1分鐘英文自我介紹就完。<br />\n中文環節: 好似係問人口老化點解決&hellip;&hellip;(唔係幾聽得清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你嗰條問乜？"},{"pid":"cff4d5c6d21d9337123b245ad8ccd23e80bd8999","tid":136302,"uid":55293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:15:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>而家係入面讀緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n讀成點？</blockquote><br />\n仆街學店<br />\n唔係教得唔好，係學校濕鳩system 有問題<br />\n佢認為我地出ward，只係識Student nurse 要做既野就夠，但係對我地真正成為一個en係醫院返工既做野係唔會教<br />\n例如：rn係唔會學抽血，打IV</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n帶返頭盔，唔教抽血、打IV係一個RN Final year既fd話我知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同學你係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}